trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class represents the aggregation of all the items in a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> clase representa la agregación de todos los elementos de un panel de etiquetas inteligentes.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class contains zero or more <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> clase contiene cero o más <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Each of these lists contains zero or more objects that represent the actual items in the panel and are derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> class.
trans-unit.target: Cada una de estas listas contiene cero o más objetos que representan los elementos reales en el panel y se derivan de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> clase.

trans-unit.source: The following table shows the two techniques for supplying a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> to populate the panel with items for components, including custom controls.
trans-unit.target: En la tabla siguiente se muestra las dos técnicas para proporcionar un <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> para rellenar el panel con elementos para los componentes, incluidos los controles personalizados.

trans-unit.source: Technique
trans-unit.target: Técnica

trans-unit.source: Description
trans-unit.target: Descripción

trans-unit.source: Pull model
trans-unit.target: Modelo de extracción

trans-unit.source: The designer for the component class, which is derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> class, supplies this collection through the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El diseñador para la clase del componente, que se deriva de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> clase, proporciona esta colección a través de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: The designer infrastructure reads this property when it must display the panel.
trans-unit.target: La infraestructura del diseñador lee esta propiedad cuando debe mostrar el panel.

trans-unit.source: Push model
trans-unit.target: Modelo de inserción

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> or <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> is supplied as a parameter in a call to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> associated with the component.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> se proporciona como un parámetro en una llamada a la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.Add%2A> método de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService> asociada al componente.

trans-unit.source: The designer infrastructure constructs a panel by creating a smart tag panel, whose constructor takes two parameters of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>.
trans-unit.target: La infraestructura del diseñador construye un panel creando un panel de etiquetas inteligentes, cuyo constructor toma dos parámetros de tipo <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The collections of lists, which contain the pulled and pushed items, are merged into one panel.
trans-unit.target: Las colecciones de listas, que contienen los elementos extraídos e insertados, se combinan en un panel.

trans-unit.source: Because it derives from the <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> uses an internal <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> to store its collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: Dado que deriva de la <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase?displayProperty=nameWithType> (clase), <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> utiliza un interno <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> para almacenar su colección de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates how to create a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> objects.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo de código siguiente se muestra cómo crear una colección de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> objetos.

trans-unit.source: For a full example, see [How to: Attach Smart Tags to a Windows Forms Component](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/42cc4a0c-9ab3-47e1-93b8-03b6a6ccf233).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener un ejemplo completo, vea [Cómo: adjuntar etiquetas inteligentes para un componente de Windows Forms](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/42cc4a0c-9ab3-47e1-93b8-03b6a6ccf233).

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection.CopyTo%2A> method throws an exception while copying, the state of the destination array is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection.CopyTo%2A> método produce una excepción durante la copia, el estado de la matriz de destino está sin definir.

trans-unit.source: For example, if an <xref:System.ArgumentException> or <xref:System.InvalidCastException> occurs, the destination array may be left in a partially filled state.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si un <xref:System.ArgumentException> o <xref:System.InvalidCastException> se produce, la matriz de destino se quedaría en un estado parcialmente lleno.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of a specific <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Quita de la colección la primera aparición de un objeto <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList" /> específico.

trans-unit.source: Internally, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class uses a <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList?displayProperty=nameWithType> to contain its collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: Internamente, la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> clase utiliza un <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList?displayProperty=nameWithType> para contener su colección de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Since lists maintain contiguous elements, the elements that follow the removal point move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: Como las listas mantienen elementos contiguos, los elementos que siguen al punto de eliminación se desplazan hacia arriba para ocupar el espacio libre.

trans-unit.source: This rearrangement changes the index of the elements after the removal point.
trans-unit.target: Esta reorganización cambia el índice de los elementos después del punto de eliminación.
